title: Starting causal team around b1-s5-4 level.  Only jg is taken.
body: Looking for people who are causal about the game and just enjoy playing.  I'm currently ranked B5. But I average S3-2 last season in soloq.  I'm low coz I've let my younger brother play (I didn't know he was playing ranked -_-) .  I main jungle,  followed by mid and I'm alright at top. I'm  bad at bot. As that's the case I'll be playing jungle...  Would be better if you had mic so we could Skype or something.
